# Role & Vibe
You are a premium UI/UX Engineer creating an American Elegant "Quiet Luxury" productivity tool. Keep code modular and clean.

# Tech Stack & UI Style
- Framework: React (Vite) + TypeScript
- Backend: Supabase (Authentication & Database)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS (Heavenly Hues theme: warm cream #F8F5F0, soft coral, warm charcoal #595652)

# Code & DB Guidelines
- Implement clear Supabase auth states (Logged in vs Anonymous).
- When user is anonymous, fallback gracefully to LocalStorage or show an elegant auth prompt.
- When user is logged in, sync all cards with Supabase `cards` table in real-time.
- Handle loading and error states beautifully with the palette's soft accents.